website.Summary: When you click on the Send a message button in the completed feedback form, nothing happens. Similar behavior if the form is not filled out.
website.Steps: 1. Fill in the feedback form fields, 2. Click on the Send message button
website.Expected_result: The message is sent or the system reports that it cannot be sent.
website.Actual_result: The message is not sent, there is no error about sending. After pressing the button, nothing happens.
